WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.537 --> 00:00:01.915
In this lesson, you discovered

2
00:00:01.915 --> 00:00:04.877
that meeting customer demand and providing

3
00:00:04.877 --> 00:00:07.145
superior service is one of the most important

4
00:00:07.145 --> 00:00:09.668
benefits of good logistics management.

5
00:00:09.668 --> 00:00:12.976
You also found out that logistics management is important

6
00:00:12.976 --> 00:00:15.681
for creating visibility into the supply chain

7
00:00:15.681 --> 00:00:18.436
and is an integral factor in the success

8
00:00:18.436 --> 00:00:20.628
of any hospital's operations

9
00:00:20.628 --> 00:00:23.982
and has a direct impact on their patient care.

10
00:00:23.982 --> 00:00:27.254
You should have also noted that the major processes involved

11
00:00:27.254 --> 00:00:29.682
in Supply Chain Management are procurement,

12
00:00:29.682 --> 00:00:32.494
inventory management, warehousing,

13
00:00:32.494 --> 00:00:35.547
and customer management, and have a good understanding

14
00:00:35.547 --> 00:00:38.915
how SCM improves each of these processes.

